name: A Saint to Fear
description:
/San La Muerte: a saint to fear.

Bless your amulet. Give him your offerings. Say your prayers, and wait.
He is the one who chooses his worshippers. 
He decides if you are worthy of the love you let slip away, he decides when your enemy will come repentant at your feet, how much you’ll win in that bet, what punishment he will impart to those who have harmed you.
Bless your amulet and bless it well, for If your enemy has a more powerful one, you will not defeat him./

𝘌𝘻𝘦 𝘔𝘢𝘵𝘵𝘦𝘰 (@𝘦𝘻𝘦_𝘮𝘢𝘵𝘵𝘦𝘰) 𝘧𝘰𝘳 𝘵𝘩𝘦 '𝘖𝘶𝘳 𝘔𝘺𝘵𝘩𝘴' 𝘦𝘹𝘩𝘪𝘣𝘪𝘵𝘪𝘰𝘯 𝘩𝘦𝘭𝘥 𝘣𝘺 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘊𝘏𝘌𝘕 𝘢𝘳𝘵𝘪𝘴𝘵 𝘤𝘰𝘭𝘭𝘦𝘤𝘵𝘪𝘷𝘦
